# Local XCFrameworks

This directory contains locally-built XCFrameworks for testing.

**These files are gitignored** - they are generated by:

```bash
cd sdk/runanywhere-commons
./backend-scripts/build-backends.sh --ios --setup-sdk
```

## Expected contents after build:
- RACommons.xcframework
- RABackendLLAMACPP.xcframework
- RABackendONNX.xcframework
- onnxruntime.xcframework
